The National Film and Video Censors Board, NFVCB, has felicitated with President Muhammadu Buhari, Vice President Professor Yemi Osinbajo and Nigerians, as they were inaugurated again for yet another four-year term. “Our future is bright, capacity is assured, and the mandate is achievable with the enigmatic, energetic, productive, unassuming and selfless leaders ALMIGHTY GOD has blessed the nation with,” read statement signed by the Executive Director of NFVCB, Alhaji Adedayo Thomas. “The excitement is visible on well-meaning Nigerians as our hopes are rekindled. It is indeed our time to move into the Next Level as a nation “We pray you greater successes and the Grace to swim the tides ahead.”